properties.description: Posted by Tracyhkim 7800 eastside road healdsburg, cahands down, my favorite winery in the RRV. Love their wines (all Burgundy-style, not the big CA fruit-forward stuff) and their beautiful property. Don’t need to call, but closed on Mondays!

properties.name: ESTATE
properties.description: Posted by Tracyhkim 400 West Spain Street Sonoma, CA 95476Every night from 5:30 or 5:45pm on, they have the most amazing deal ever: 0 for a glass of pinot noir or pinot gris and a wood fired pizza. The deal only works at their bar, on the patio (not to be confused w/ their outdoor seating), or at one AMAZING table in their outdoor seating area just in front of the fireplace. It\'s my new way to end a great day of wine tasting in Sonoma – highly recommend it
